Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Cambridge sub-lease available right off of Highway 401 with excellent exposure. 1180 SF professional office space with 4 individuals offices, reception space and server room. Accessible space with ample parking.

Finished office space & warehouse area in a newly renovated building near Highway #401. Unit 1-2 is 2,282 sq. ft. with an additional 634 sq.ft. of mezzanine at a discounted rate. Space includes a built out washroom, kitchenette, private offices & reception area. 950 sq.ft. warehouse area at 16' clear. Upgraded building facade & roof with new windows and doors for low utility costs. Ample on-site parking & 10' x 10' drive- in door at rear of unit for loading.

6,100 sq. ft. of institutional office available for lease. Located within a 5 minute drive of Highway 401. 1.4 acres of access land available on site. Site is free and clear from environmental concerns along with building free of material defects.
6,351 to 23,626 SF office space available for lease. Located minutes from Highway 401 in Cambridge, ON, approx. 35 mins from GTA.
